{"word":"H7025 - קִיר חֶרֶשׂ - Qîyr Cheres - keer kheh'-res - Kir-haraseth","slug":"H7025","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">קִיר חֶרֶשׂ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Qîyr Cheres"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>keer kheh'-res"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Kir-haraseth"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E7;&#x05D9;&#x05E8; &#x05D7;&#x05E8;&#x05E9;&#x05C2;&#x05EA;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E7;&#x05D9;&#x05E8; &#x05D7;&#x05E8;&#x05E9;&#x05C2; - q&#x0131;&#x0302;yr cheres&#x0301;  q&#x0131;&#x0302;yr cha&#x0306;res&#x0301;eth</b> - <i>(keer) kheh'-res, khar-eh'-seth</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H7023\">H7023</a> and <a href=\"#/H2789\">H2789</a>; <i>fortress of earthenware</i>; <i>Kir-Cheres</i> or <i>Kir-Chares-eth</i>, a place in Moab: - Kir-haraseth, Kir-hareseth, Kir-haresh, Kir-heres."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H6972\">H6972</a>, <a href=\"#/H7019\">H7019</a>, <a href=\"#/H7021\">H7021</a>, <a href=\"#/H7023\">H7023</a>, <a href=\"#/H7024\">H7024</a>, <a href=\"#/H7027\">H7027</a>, <a href=\"#/H7028\">H7028</a>"}]}